'''Charles Nicolas François Brisout de Barneville<ref>Société entomologique de France.  [https://books.google.com/books?id=SZTyAAAAMAAJ&pg=PR33 ''Annales de la Société Entomologique de France'', Volume 64]</ref>''' (22 July 1822, in [[Paris]] &ndash; 2 May 1893, in [[St. Germain-en-Laye]]) was a [[France|French]] [[entomologist]] who specialised in [[Orthoptera]] and [[Coleoptera]].

He was President of the [[Société entomologique de France]] in 1873. His collections are kept by the Society.

